    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014practically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and the interior is still spotless. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have\u2014I'd love for this car to go to a great new home!",
