    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically superlative E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated straight-six, with the high-pressure double-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. The six individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, while the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile, precise shifts. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the limited-slip differential remains tight and silent. Finished in original paint with an immaculate undercarriage, this vehicle has been maintained to the highest standard, ensuring the chassis dynamics and engine harmonics are as sharp as the day it left Regensburg.",
      "price": 44500.0,
