    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, and has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent is still present. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full-service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. The engine bay is detailed and pristine, reflecting the low-mileage care this vehicle has received. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a bespoke car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
