    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in pristine condition and looking like it just stepped off the showroom floor. It drives like a dream and is honestly as close to perfect as a used car gets. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, so if you're looking for something that's been loved and kept spotless, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
