    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pinnacle specimen for the purist, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically impeccable, this chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement with VAC Motorsports components. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity and torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the telepathic steering rack feedback these cars are celebrated for. With zero fluid leaks and compression numbers holding steady across all cylinders, this collector-grade vehicle offers a turn-key experience for the serious enthusiast.",
